Detailed Description

This class implements the Stack of Task. It allows to deal with the priority of the controllers through the shell. The controllers can be either constraints either tasks.

This class defines the basic elements of a task. A task is defined as where is a set of features and the actuated joints of the robot.
It is assume that . Moreover as it assumed that this task can provide: It then possible to compute with , and the desired feature and the one currently measured.

It is possible to add features or clear the list of features. This class makes also possible to select some of the listed of features to compute the control law through setControlSelection, addControlSelection, clearControlSelection.
